    <item>
      <title>Original publication date in Zotero</title>
      <link>https://rmatv.github.io/en/2022/05/zotero_origdate/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 May 2022 01:45:04 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://rmatv.github.io/en/2022/05/zotero_origdate/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Fill &amp;lsquo;Extra&amp;rsquo; field in Zotero with &lt;code&gt;original-date: (year)&lt;/code&gt; to include
original publication date in a reference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For example: &lt;a href=&#34;https://archive.org/details/sportwork0000riga&#34;&gt;English edition&lt;/a&gt;
of &lt;em&gt;Sport und Arbeit&lt;/em&gt; by Bero Rigauer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;images/zotero_origdate/rigauer_zotero.png&#34; width=&#34;75%&#34;/&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;
            &lt;h4&gt;Fields in Zotero&lt;/h4&gt;
        &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Zotero creates a correct reference depending on style:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;images/zotero_origdate/example_apa.png&#34;/&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;
            &lt;h4&gt;APA 6th (LibreOffice)&lt;/h4&gt;
        &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;images/zotero_origdate/example_asa.png&#34;/&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;
            &lt;h4&gt;ASA 7th (LibreOffice)&lt;/h4&gt;
        &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This setting also works for exporting citations to BibLaTeX using
Better BibTeX extension:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;
&lt;table style=&#34;border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 7
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 8
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 9
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;10
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;11
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;12
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;13
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bibtex&#34; data-lang=&#34;bibtex&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#458;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;@book&lt;/span&gt;{&lt;span style=&#34;color:#900;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;rigauer1981&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{Sport and Work}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;author&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{Rigauer, Bero}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;translator&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{Guttman, Allen}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;date&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{1981}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;origdate&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{1969}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;series&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{European {{Perspectives}}}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;publisher&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{{Columbia University Press}}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;location&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{{New York}}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;isbn&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{978-0-231-05200-9}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;langid&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{english}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#008080&#34;&gt;pagetotal&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;{xxxiv, 127}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;images/zotero_origdate/example_latex.png&#34;/&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;
            &lt;h4&gt;APA 6th (BibLaTeX)&lt;/h4&gt;
        &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have found this tip on Zotero &lt;a href=&#34;https://forums.zotero.org/discussion/63774/original-dates-of-publication&#34;&gt;forum discussion&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
